      <t>In an SRv6 network, each SRv6 Segment Endpoint Node must be assigned an SRv6 Locator, and segment IDs are generated within the address space of this SRv6 Locator. This document describes a method for assigning SRv6 Locators to SRv6 Segment Endpoint Nodes through DHCPv6.</t>
